	<p><strong>2. Contest Description</strong><br>Half Past Now will conduct a random drawing from the pool of all eligible participants who enter the contest prior to the Entry Deadline Date (defined below). The person selected will win the prize described in detail below.</p>

	<p><strong>3. Selecting a Winner</strong><br>Half Past Now will select the name of the winner by random drawing on October 8th from the pool of all eligible entries received by the Entry Deadline Date (as further defined below). Emmis Austin Radio will then contact the person selected by phone and notify the person that he/she wins the prize below. The odds of winning vary depending upon the number of eligible entries received.</p>
	
