	<p><strong>5. How to Enter</strong><br>Beginning September 18th 2013, eligible participants may register as follows:
By App. Download the free Half Past Now phone app. Open the app, click on the Mneu icon in the top left corner. Click on the Me icon, and either register by Facebook or email address.<br><br>
